    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎游玩《GRIDbeat!》！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>在这款节奏驱动的赛博地牢探索游戏中，每一个动作都必须与音乐协调一致，稍有差错就会导致系统全面宕机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你已经成功突破了克诺斯操作系统——这颗星球最固若金汤的企业网络，并准备带着价值连城的数据逃离。但此刻，你被困在系统内部，遭到失控的安全协议和充满敌意的恶意程序围追堵截。想要突出重围，只有一条路：与系统同步，踩准节拍移动，在网格将你永久封锁之前，寻找逃生之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>节拍驱动的地牢探险</strong> <br>在《GRIDbeat!》中，无论是移动、战斗还是互动，都需要踩准节拍。每个关卡都是一场节奏即生存的战术挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/12df3163cf818e98ef483998bdc184f4.poster.avif?t=1772150233\" width=780 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/12df3163cf818e98ef483998bdc184f4.webm?t=1772150233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/12df3163cf818e98ef483998bdc184f4.mp4?t=1772150233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扣人心弦的迷宫探索</strong> <br>在数据迷宫中穿梭时，你必须时刻警惕各类危险，尤其要当心那些能将整个关卡数据清除的服务器格式化程序。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/0f258ca5a2d5329b1c5e933346556128.poster.avif?t=1772150233\" width=780 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/0f258ca5a2d5329b1c5e933346556128.webm?t=1772150233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/0f258ca5a2d5329b1c5e933346556128.mp4?t=1772150233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进化技能与强化道具</strong> <br>安装功能强大的软件工具，助你抵御系统威胁，揭开隐藏机密，化解重重难关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/eee5478416a56d109741c0989a39701a.poster.avif?t=1772150233\" width=780 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/eee5478416a56d109741c0989a39701a.webm?t=1772150233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/eee5478416a56d109741c0989a39701a.mp4?t=1772150233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与赛博意识首领决战</strong> <br>在酣畅淋漓的节奏激战中，击败强大AI守卫，继续你的征程，最终抵达主机的最终出口端口。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/5e9a53ec8af5c3b3b0891275c612837f.poster.avif?t=1772150233\" width=780 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/5e9a53ec8af5c3b3b0891275c612837f.webm?t=1772150233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/5e9a53ec8af5c3b3b0891275c612837f.mp4?t=1772150233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>投身节奏之中！</strong> <br>《GRIDbeat!》的劲爆电子音乐将让你全身心投入战斗，每次移动、每项技能、每记攻击都将随着节拍跃动。让你的操作与音乐同步，让律动引领你穿梭网格、所向披靡！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/27e52be1b0202020ec077adec73fd042.poster.avif?t=1772150233\" width=780 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/27e52be1b0202020ec077adec73fd042.webm?t=1772150233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243370/extras/27e52be1b0202020ec077adec73fd042.mp4?t=1772150233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
